 * ║        AetherAI ESP32 Voice Agent — Config Template          ║
 * ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
 * ║  SETUP:                                                      ║
 * ║   1. Copy this file → voice_config.h                         ║
 * ║   2. Fill in your WiFi, Railway, and ByteDance values below  ║
 * ║   3. voice_config.h is in .gitignore — never committed       ║
 * ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
